**Priority recommendation:** Fix #1 first — it reduces struct size by 3×, eliminates 5 divisions per arithmetic op, and benefits every part of the pipeline (arithmetic, comparison, formatting). Fix #2 next if profiling confirms `ToString` is called per-transfer per-tick.
